Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:04.35,Fujimiya Girls' High School,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fujimiya Girls' High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:11.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a month \Nsince school started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, have you gotten used to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Our theater society is still going on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't do well \Nin front of people, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:27.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I have you, Mayu-chan, \NKuu-chan, and our landlady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And I've made friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:32.88,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morn—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:34.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,...ing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.14,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.18,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are they friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:22.99,sign_3309_17_Scarecrow_Heroin,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Scarecrow Heroine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.70,sign_3429_18_Theater_Club,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Theater Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:27.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll begin our \Nfull practice in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you all do your warm-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:32.08,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.98,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm just curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a child in the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:45.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she's been \Ncoming here for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:50.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,None of the other members \Nhave said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:57.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it seems like they've been practicing \Na lot harder these past few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady seems that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:04.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's standing next to \Nthe landlady, could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,...a theater troupe relation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so well-developed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not the landlady's daughter, is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How old would she have\Nbeen when she had her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You know who that girl is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:28.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's Kuroyanagi Ruriko, \Na famous child actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen her on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.27,Italics Dialogue Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Now for our next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We only had three channels back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.79,Italics Dialogue Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.08,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroyanagi Ruriko is only nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but her acting rivals that of any adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:49.29,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's a super celebrity said to \Ncome along only once every century!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:53.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The contrast between her cool personality \Nand passionate acting is part of her charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan, you're very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Were you even listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.05,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,(Woman)Countess: Now, why don't we sing? To enjoy this night, this moment, the present.\NIsn't that what people do?\N-The countess looks around, giving Pino a menacing glare\N(Man)Pino: But there is no heart here. How are we supposed to sing without heart? How are we supposed to enjoy that?\N-Trio flinches slightly, but manages a word\N(Woman)Countess: But there is heart.\N-Delzoi, without losing heart\N(Man)Delzoi: But where? I can't see it at all. You say something that doesn't exist, exists, \Nand something that does exist, actually doesn't. You're quite difficult, aren't you?\N-Countess, while giving a mysterious smile\N(Woman)Countess: Right now... Right now, there isn't. There's no way there could be.\N-Pino, interrupting\N(Man)Pino: Then why is singing...\N-Duchess, without any agitation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.05,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kuroyanagi Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:13.60,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here as a special instructor \Nto serve as this club's advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.19,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I returned to Japan recently \Nafter completing my theater training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:23.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean she's \Nthe advisor we heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:27.83,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's her fault the\N theater club was forced into hiatus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.37,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.54,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.75,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I cast aside my job \Nas this theater club's advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:43.49,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I was beginning to lose \Nmy confidence and motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:47.01,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,to teach and guide \Nall of you as your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.64,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe she's nine years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:55.14,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,So I went overseas to \Nlearn theater from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.74,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The Palais Garnier, La Scala, \Nthe Vienna State Opera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:04.03,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I visited theaters in many countries,\N and met many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.52,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,In doing so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned what is most important \Nas both an actor and a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:15.08,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I returned to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:19.42,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to show \Nthe fruits of my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,On TV? In movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.80,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.55,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,In this theater club's performance \Nat the upcoming culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,After you went all the way \Nto Europe to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.31,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I went there to train as \Nan advisor, and nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The culture festival is in one month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.64,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, let's eat lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.45,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so the club's advisor is back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll go back to being \Nthe theater club again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had some things to think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.24,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so she wants it to remain \Na society for the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.72,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:15.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But the members must be \Nreally psyched up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:15.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.98,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see Hina-chan \Nand the Kuu-chan practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.24,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,In the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:31.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She practices in her room \Nevery day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like her vocal practices with Kuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And stretches...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.94,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to see the results \Nof that firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's not getting it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan... you were able \Nto do it at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:13.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many club members, \Nit makes me nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.39,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:20.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You know how they say to imagine people \Nas vegetables when you're nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.29,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like pumpkins, or daikon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Daikon? Pumpkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.68,Main Dialogue,Pumpkin,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin-kin-kin-kin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.94,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? If I freeze up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:55.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you use these steps for this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, you're such a good dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.78,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That should work, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm g-g-going—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.05,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Join our performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.16,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A girl as cute as you \Nwill become a star in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:45.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not good at that \Nsort of... I mean... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:50.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She caught Hina-chan's scarecrow problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.80,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.31,Main Dialogue Top,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.81,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're all practicing, \Nbut please stop for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:11.03,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something \NI'd like all of you to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The advisor has something to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.58,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.46,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Please play this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.65,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.61,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,All right, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:16.58,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Walking home on a starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:21.97,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,All alone, I start to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.75,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:28.42,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll softly wipe my tears away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:25.23,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:33.77,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Then look up at the light and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.82,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Shining star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:40.65,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes, when they begin to sparkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:45.28,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Are just like the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:55.13,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, born to make my dream shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:11:03.77,Main Dialogue Top,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Shining star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you're a great singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:24.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.53,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I always sang
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"La, la, la, la" to call red foxes back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.37,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What part of the country \Ndid Hina-chan come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere up north?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:06.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.65,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your black tea and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me \Nthis morning, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:23.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a resident of Hitotose Manor, \NI need to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have many customers yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:27.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There are no customers left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:38.64,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should have \Nsome more around lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.66,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:48.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go get ice cream \Nfrom the place by the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm going to a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.42,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I finally grabbed an empty seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You should hang out with me sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.30,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important \Nto you, me or theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.35,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the coffee shop for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.20,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We had more lunch customers than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You were a big help, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:43.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you wanted attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.73,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't treat me like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to spend time \Nwith the landlady today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should've just \Ngone to the play with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.91,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess you can't \Nleave me in charge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in theater, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the small theater troupe \NAki-chan went to see today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.71,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,only does horror shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:32.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And their lead actress \Nalways acts so realistically
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:36.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,that a lot of people say they can't sleep \Nthe night after seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you know a lot about it, \Nhuh, Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I just got curious \Nand looked into it a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what they call "being interested"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say whether I'm \Ninterested or not, maybe I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But theater is all Aki-chan ever talks about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're just at a difficult age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to treat me like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is that lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.24,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were you having \Nso much fun talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you could hear us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just faintly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:29.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady is infatuated with theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:32.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and, um... Mayu-chan wanted to get \Nsome ice cream by the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:36.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and Mayu-chan isn't interested in theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm not really sure anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You don't have to talk about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:49.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, she's jealous of theater because \Nthe landlady never has time for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you figure it out from that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:04.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that the reason why you said \Nyou didn't want to be in theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:04.94,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.44,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan loses sight of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she really does love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And the club's advisor just came back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:20.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm happy that she's motivated \Nagain because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:26.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But that also means she pays \Nno attention to me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:29.96,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wish she wouldn't \Nget so absorbed in theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A maiden's heart is a complex thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:37.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fill that hole in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:45.92,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you both doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady sure is late getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And she just left the shop like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,When she gets back, \NI'm gonna let her have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady isn't obligated \Nto work here, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I brought this back as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the place by the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.29,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.76,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't had time to hang out lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have ice cream together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:28.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:31.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,They're like a mother and child. \NHow heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,They look like some goofy couple to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.84,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.96,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,in each country, theater is searching \Nfor new forms of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.71,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We need to polish our acting every day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't fall behind, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The results of your studies abroad \Nare pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.10,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.94,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Studying abroad greatly \Nstimulated my creative urges,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.76,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,so I wrote these scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.53,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest masterpiece of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.78,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We will perform this at the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.78,sign_26348_276_And_Everyone_Is_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,And Everyone Is Part of \Nthe ABC Tragedy Case File!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This could be my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:30.29,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! If I'm chosen to play \Nthe heroine in this masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.07,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,You, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to play the heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You meant her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:01.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Me? The heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.70,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.95,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.83,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&}Direction 6: After standing one 1.8 meter pole and one 2.7 meter pole\N straight up until they reached the bottom of the pool, the difference in \Nlength above the water's surface was 2:5. \NWrite how deep the pool is in meters, including the decimal value.\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}-No idea\N{\c&H000000&}-Small!\N-Long legs\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.83,Note - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7C1CD2&}-Jiggle\N-Bunny with beautiful legs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:11.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm a new member, and I don't \Nknow anything about acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right! I'm a \Nbetter actress than she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:18.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako is just a ham actor \Nwith no talent or experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:23.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The point is, this failshrimp \Ncan't play the heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.30,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:29.16,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The image I have in mind for \Nthe heroine is perfect for Hinako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Image?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:33.83,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like her singing and her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.41,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,And her proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.26,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You were hand-picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.75,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:54.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll... t-try my besht...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.74,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I did that to you without warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:13.32,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted you to be my heroine so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:19.23,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely confident in this script.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.38,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make it the perfect production,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.86,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just like I envisioned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:31.62,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,And I need your help to do that, Hinako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So don't cry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:42.14,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.43,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Today's club goal!\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}-Make sure the club journal is published in time\NDeadline is strict!\N-Let's give the advisor a report at least 3 days in advance\NSensei, sorry to always keep you waiting\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.43,Note - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping list\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}-B5 copy paper\N-Screen tones\N-Copics\NBuy? *Negotiable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:49.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Hina-chan was picked \Nto play the lead, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:00.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Will I really be able to play the heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.95,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on what you do \Nfrom here, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:07.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it depends on \Nhow much I practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:10.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we practice right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I did get the script.
